{"tid":1878041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【Over My Dead Body】律師彼此看不爽怒丟炸彈　印度法院爆炸多人受傷","createTime":"2020-02-13T11:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T05:53:34.000Z","uid":29188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"896a0687d2f961b5fb90a61e287f33cf01c4a250","tid":1878041,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"記者丁維瑀／綜合報導<br />\n《新德里電視台》報導，印度北方邦（Uttar Pradesh）首府勒克瑙（Lucknow）一處法院今（13）日下午發生爆炸事件，造成至少兩名律師受傷，目擊者表示，在現場起碼發現2枚炸彈。《今日印度》指出，據了解，疑似是兩團不同的律師代表發生爭執，才會導致這起事件。<br />\n根據《今日印度》（INDIA TODAY），勒克瑙一處法院今日傳來爆炸聲響，詳細地點位於Hazratganj，靠近當地地方法官的辦公室，其中有一人受到重傷，另外兩人則是輕傷。當地消息指出，有兩派律師團出現爭執，接著就有爆炸聲響，疑似是為了攻擊法庭上的律師所為。<br />\n勒克瑙律師協會聯合秘書長洛迪（Sanjeev Lodhi）聲稱，自己是被攻擊的目標。警方已確認，利用炸彈進行攻擊的是亞達夫（Jeetu Yadav），疑似使用當地所製造的爆炸裝置。當局正在調查這起事件時，警方又在現場發現3枚炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 快訊／律師彼此看不爽怒丟炸彈　印度法院爆炸多人受傷 | ETtoday國際新聞 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 | ETtoday MobileWeb <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200213/1644845.htm#ixzz6Dpb4uAuf \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200213%2F1644845.htm%23ixzz6Dpb4uAuf%20&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvcsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=907a905c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200213/1644845.htm#ixzz6Dpb4uAuf </a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"92fe21e34913199c998fefddba34637f70e9b596","tid":1878041,"uid":77196,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"Over My Dead Body<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdc26b9e61cbf9791a159414aaf00e4cbf64a55","tid":1878041,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233d5aeed9d87d17ee40ff2a5aed77934c4e1538","tid":1878041,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"@楊岳橋"},{"pid":"46d733e53b2c346c8a62f0292fb5388505065f81","tid":1878041,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f93d5a3c8ef08c0602055021d1b411d56001250","tid":1878041,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf28978ae8706c54bad0e6ddf13b4788e51bc50","tid":1878041,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"個法官平時係威係勢 見到汽油蛋米係要走"},{"pid":"996bf5401338a0c7e3fa5e99511a544b9a7a2ae0","tid":1878041,"uid":210140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我有一個大膽的想法</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"82a5d976b10b5631199b5f1d07cf8dbeae4bf450","tid":1878041,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"仲要係律師掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}